&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create and maintain a library of enablement materials—quick-start guides, prompt engineering playbooks, video walkthroughs, FAQs, and best-practice documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
