&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Track and report on adoption metrics—usage, engagement, satisfaction, and business impact—to measure progress and identify gaps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
